Ubus example setup (ubus_tb_top.sv)

ubus_if vif();			// ubus_if interface
dut_dummy dut(...) ;		//  dut 
test testbench_blk();		//  program block with uvm tests and verification environment 

Partitioning scheme (ubus_topcfg.v)

        partition package uvm_pkg;	// partition for uvm_pkg
        partition cell dut_dummy;	// partition for dut block 
        partition cell test;		// partition for test block 

Recompilation scenario 

During recompilation step we are adding a new test in test block. 

Recompilation behavior 

Addition of new test will trigger the recompilation of only test partition and other partitions will not recompiled.

To run the example:
	Use Makefile
